    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.immortal-ardor.equipment.Item.yKMUD1HOmeOgBCq4]{Artisan's Soup Pot}</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">After you eat a serving of soup, its effects last 24 hours or until you make your next daily preparations, whichever comes first. You gain a +1 item bonus to checks made to Craft or Repair, or increase any existing item bonus for these checks by 1. You also restore an additional 5 Hit Points per item bonus to items you successfully Repair during this time.</span></p><p>If you eat a serving of Artisan's Soup for each workday required to attempt a check to Craft, the item bonus from the soup can be applied to that check, too.</p>"
